item.title: Classic VW Restorations
item.description: Overview Project created for a local auto shop specializing in Classic Volkswagons out of Fullerton CA. classicvws.shop is built on WordPress using the popular site builder plugin Elementor Pro. Hosted on an AWS EC2 Instance using Bitnami Wordpress AMI Toolset emphasizes design over development Migration (Note to Self): Make sure to associate an elasticIP before pointing a Domain Name at the incstance’s public IP. Live database overwritten by exporting localhost.
